1
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:10,800
I heard the array is right inside the Maritime Garrison

2
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:53,400
Celestial Pivot Wave-Calm

3
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:54,800
Tianxuan Wave-Splitter

4
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:56,080
Celestial Pearl Suppresses Calamity

5
00:00:56,080 --> 00:00:57,280
Celestial Scale Pacifies the Tide

6
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:59,080
In ancient times, seven stars suppressed the Heavenly River

7
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:00,840
Today, the North Dipper suppresses the ocean waves

8
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,040
North Dipper Wave-Calming Array

9
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:04,760
Rise

10
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:25,400
Li Jing

11
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,880
The array's power is exhausted

12
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,920
It cannot be used again in the short term

13
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,640
How long is this "short term"

14
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,400
At least three years

15
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,200
Darn it

16
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,400
We've been tricked

17
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,920
Tricked

18
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:47,440
When the Sea Clan attacks

19
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,680
will they give us three years

20
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,000
No

21
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:53,400
The Sea Clan arranging Xu Zhong to hold a living sacrifice

22
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,000
was just a smokescreen

23
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:55,920
Darn

24
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,040
This is a conspiracy

25
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,200
They deliberately lured us into activating the array

26
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,400
Besides this one

27
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,920
does Chentang Pass have any other arrays

28
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,680
An array of this power

29
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:07,160
requires at least ten top-tier cultivators

30
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:09,520
and decades of time to barely set up

31
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,960
How could there be a second one

32
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,480
Two things

33
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:13,760
What things

34
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:14,920
First

35
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:15,960
Go to the Eye of the Abyss

36
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,160
Find the Nine-River Dragon Pivot

37
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,000
The Sea Clan values it so much

38
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,040
there must be a reason

39
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,800
It might be some kind of treasure

40
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:23,400
that can help us defend Chentang Pass

41
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,240
And the other thing

42
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,320
The other thing is

43
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,480
light the Beacon tower to ask Zhaoge for reinforcements

44
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,880
But

45
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,960
without the Commander's order token

46
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:33,320
the Beacon tower guard definitely won't light the fire

47
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,640
You're too rigid in your thinking

48
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,760
Can't we just take his token and issue the order

49
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,040
This

50
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,000
is against the rules

51
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,000
At a time like this

52
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,680
will following the rules save Chentang Pass

53
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,320
You're right

54
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,120
As long as we can save Chentang Pass

55
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,240
even if I violate military law

56
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,240
I, Li Jing, am willing to bear full responsibility

57
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,400
Halt

58
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,440
Who goes there

59
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,200
By order of the Commander

60
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,440
You are ordered to light the beacon immediately

61
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,880
Do not disobey

62
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,200
Are you General Li Jing

63
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,920
I haven't had the honor of meeting you before, General

64
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:18,320
General Li's heroic defense of Chentang Pass is known to all

65
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,960
We admire you greatly

66
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:20,960
Brother

67
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,200
We have urgent military intelligence

68
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,800
We need to commandeer a grey goose

69
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:25,960
Follow me

70
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,640
It's so beautiful

71
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,480
Yes

72
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,280
Your Highness

73
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,520
Report from the front

74
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,560
The Fire Snake plan has succeeded

75
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:13,400
Your Highness is wise

76
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:17,360
However, the Crab soldiers who infiltrated Chentang Pass

77
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,880
have lost contact

78
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:21,200
I fear they are doomed

79
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,760
Useless trash

80
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,640
Send the order

81
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:25,320
Execute one hundred thousand of the Crab Clan

82
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,240
As a warning to others

83
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,320
Yes, sir

84
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,480
Also

85
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:34,520
Tell Si Meng to take people to patrol near the Abyss

86
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,920
If any humans are found

87
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:41,200
destroy their primordial spirits immediately

88
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,160
The map shows it's right here

89
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:49,960
Look over there

90
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,200
Yes

91
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:52,960
Sancai Island

92
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,240
We've arrived

93
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,840
Brother Goose, please wait here

94
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:57,960
If within three days

95
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:59,480
the two of us have not returned

96
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,280
Brother Goose

97
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:01,560
please return to Chentang Pass on your own

98
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:06,760
Water Repelling Pearl

99
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,520
This is the time to use it, right

100
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,320
This fish is so cute.

101
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:28,800
Don't move.

102
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,920
It is a deadly beauty.

103
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,040
A creature of deadly poison.

104
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:32,880
Alright, alright.

105
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,800
I understand.

106
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,240
Did you hear something?

107
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,920
Could it be...

108
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,480
Run!

109
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,600
Five Thunders Orthodox Law!
